<HEADLINE>
KOSOVO: TRUCE OR CONSEQUENCES  
 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (ATTN: Commentary Editors)   (This excellent 850-word ``separate buy'' article is from the
current (week beginning 6 February 1999) Economist magazine.)  
  
 (EDITORS: We regret that this material is NOT available to clients
