<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-02-06 12:43 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A4411 &Cx1f; tta-z
u i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-KOSOVO-TALKS-965(2TAK     02-06 1003
</HEADER>
