   IMPEACH-CAMPAIGN (Boston) _ The reluctance of Republican
presidential prospects to weigh in enthusiastically _ or at all _
on the president's impeachment trial underscores their party's
ambivalence about how impeachment is playing politically. By
Richard L. Berke.
