<HEADLINE>
POWER IN JORDAN PASSES TO KING HUSSEIN'S SON 
</HEADLINE>
  
 (Repeating to add photo advisory)  (See also JORDAN-PRINCE, JORDAN-CANCER)  
 (ART ADV: Photo is being sent to NYT photo clients.
