</P>
<P>
   DAILY WEATHER
</P>
<P>
   2/7 COLOR WEATHER -- 3 x 4 1/4 -- National forecast map in color
</P>
<P>
   2/7 B&AMP;W WEATHER -- 3 x 4 1/4 -- National forecast map
</P>
<P>
   2/7 CLOUD COVER -- 15p x 1 7/8 --Predicted cloud cover each day
</P>
